---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Time Zone Calculator"
  description="Privacy Poilicy for tzcompare.com"
  keywords=""
  canonicalURL="https://tzcompare.com/privacy-policy"
  robots="index, follow"
>
  <main class="p-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4"><i class="material-icons mr-1">article</i>Privacy Policy</h1>
    
        <p>Effective Date: April 14, 2025</p>
    
        <p>
          At <strong>TZCompare</strong>, we take your privacy seriously.
          This Privacy Policy outlines what information we collect, how we use it,
          and your rights regarding that information.
        </p>
    
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">
          1. Information We Do Not Collect
        </h2>
        <p>
          We do <strong>not collect</strong> any personally identifiable information
          (PII), IP addresses, location data, cookies, or usage data from users. Your
          interactions with the time zone calculator take place entirely within your browser
          and are not stored or transmitted anywhere.
        </p>
    
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">
          2. Use of Third-Party Tools
        </h2>
        <p>
          At this time, we do not use third-party analytics or tracking tools. If we
          choose to implement analytics (e.g., Google Analytics) in the future to
          improve user experience, this policy will be updated accordingly, and a
          notice will be provided.
        </p>
    
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">3. External Links</h2>
        <p>
          This site may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible
          for the content or privacy practices of those websites. We encourage users
          to read the privacy policies of any external sites they visit.
        </p>
    
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">
          4. Changes to This Privacy Policy
        </h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be
          posted on this page with an updated effective date. We encourage users to
          check this page periodically for any updates.
        </p>
    
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">5. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please
          contact us at:
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong> info@tzcompare.com
        </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

